OL,3,CMoonpig considers options as funding
OL,4,Cpulled for Guernsey mail plane
OL,6,FOnline-based gift business Moonpig
OL,7,Fsays it is actively looking at other
OL,8,Fdelivery options after Royal Mail
OL,9,Fannounced that it will end its
OL,10,Ffinancial contribution to Guernsey's
OL,11,Fdaily mail plane.
OL,13,FGuernsey Post and Royal Mail currently
OL,14,Fcontribute equally to the air service
OL,15,Fwhich exports around four to six
OL,16,Ftonnes of letters and small parcels
OL,17,Fdaily.
