OL,6,FHowever, Royal Mail is cutting ties
OL,7,Ffrom April 2025 as part of a need to
OL,8,Freduce costs across its network -
OL,9,Fsimilar decisions were taken in Jersey
OL,10,Fand the Isle of Man last year.
OL,12,FMoonpig sold more than 48 million
OL,13,Fgreeting cards and gifts globally in
OL,14,Fthe 2023-24 financial year with 82% of
OL,15,Fits revenue coming from the United
OL,16,FKingdom.
