OL,3,CMoonpig considers options as funding
OL,4,Cpulled for Guernsey mail plane
OL,6,FThe business runs a large part of its
OL,7,FBritish operations from Guernsey with
OL,8,Frival gifting company Funky Pigeon
OL,9,Falso delivering services from the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FA Moonpig spokesperson says: "We are
OL,13,Fdoing everything we can to find an
OL,14,Falternative arrangement following
OL,15,FRoyal Mail's recent announcement.
OL,17,F"We have been working closely with
OL,18,FGuernsey Post to find a solution that
OL,19,Fwill enable the continuation of this
OL,20,Fservice."
