OL,6,FITV News has contacted Funky Pigeon
OL,7,Ffor comment and did not immediately
OL,8,Freceive a response.
OL,10,FMany smaller local businesses and
OL,11,Fresidents also rely on the quick
OL,12,Fdelivery times that the mail plane
OL,13,Foffers.
OL,15,FGuernsey Post Chief Executive Boley
OL,16,FSmillie says: "We were informed of
OL,17,FRoyal Mail's change in position
OL,18,Fearlier this year, which was
OL,19,Fdisappointing news.
